Interface Fadable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Pogo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PogoImage

    public interface Fadable
    Author:
    Todd Url This interface designates that its implementor can adjust it's opacity from transparent to opaque or from opaque to transparent over a configurable amount of time.
